<abstract>
<t>The Point-to-Point Protocol (PPP) [provides a standard method for transporting multi-protocol datagrams over point-to-point links. The PPP Compression Control Protocolprovides a method to negotiate and utilize compression protocols over PPP encapsulated links.</t>
<t>This document describes the use of the Gandalf FZA data compression algorithmfor compressing PPP encapsulated packets.</t></abstract></front>

